   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1654_dai_lns235ms_j_r.jpg"/> 
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre"> 
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1"  xml:id="trans_div1"><p>God is great</p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>چودهریان و قانونوگویان و مقدمان و  رعایا پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               را اعلام آنکه
               <lb/>تالابی که متصل موضع
               <placeName ref="#naugaon">نوگانوہ</placeName>
               و
               <placeName ref="#khilchipur">قلچی پور</placeName>
               معموله پرگنه مذکور است متعلق به اراضی
               <lb/><placeName ref="#naugaon">نوگانوہ</placeName>
               و
               <placeName ref="#khilchipur">قلچی پور</placeName>
               از قدیم الایام تا حال بوده و می باشد در این وقت رعایای موضع  
               <lb/><placeName ref="#tornod">ترنود</placeName>
               اراده نموده که آب تالاب را به آراضی ده خود برده زراعت نمایند  
               <lb/>بنا بر ین نوشته می شود که احدی  بهیچ وجه دخل  بآب تالاب سوی رعایای که  
               <lb/>از قدیم متصرف بوده ننماید و مزاحم بحال آنها نرساند و خود را شریک و بهم  
               <lb/>در آن تالاب نشمارند که موجب تنبیہ  و تادیب ایشان می گردد و پته مقرر نموده که<note>The text continues onto the right margin.</note>
               <lb/>موازی
               <measure type="land" unit="bigha" quantity="10">ده بیگہ</measure>
               زمین شنکر هر سال سوای جمع
               <lb/>در موضع
               <placeName ref="#naugaon">نوگنده</placeName>
               نگارد تحریر
               <date calendar="#julus"><num>۴</num> 
               صفر سنه
               <num>۲۸</num></date>
               <lb/>حسب المسطور عمل نمایند
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
            
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2"  xml:id="trans_div2">  
            <p>
               <lb/>It is announced to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhris</ref> and <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungos</ref> and <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muqaddam">muqaddams</ref> and subjects of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> that  
               <lb/>the tank adjoining the villages of <placeName ref="#naugaon">Naugaon</placeName> and <placeName ref="#khilchipur">Qilchipur [Khilchipur]</placeName>, [which are] under the administration of the said <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>, has been and shall be dedicated to the agricultural lands of  
               <lb/><placeName ref="#naugaon">Naugaon</placeName> and <placeName ref="#khilchipur">Qilchipur [Khilchipur]</placeName> from the olden days until now. At the present time, the subjects of the village
               <lb/><placeName ref="#tornod">Tornod</placeName> have demonstrated their intention to seize the water of the tank for the land in their own village and undertake agriculture.
               <lb/>Based on this, let it be written that no one should, for any reason, take possession of the water of the tank other than the subjects who
               <lb/>since olden times had been in possession [of the tank], and should not cause obstacles to their [the subjects’] situation and should not count themselves among the partners [co-owners] 
               <lb/>of this tank and not become the reason for chastisement and correction. And a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_patta">patta</ref> was issued that  
               <lb/><measure type="land" unit="bigha" quantity="10">ten bighas</measure> of land should be preserved tax-free every year in the village <placeName ref="#naugaon">Naugaon</placeName>.
               <lb/>Written on the <date calendar="#julus">4th of Safar in the year 28</date>.
               <lb/>Do as written. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g><note>This final line can be read as part of the authorisation.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal"><mentioned><persName ref="#mirIbrahim">ابراهیم</persName>
                  بنده صدق سلطان 
                  <persName ref="#muradBakhsh">مراد بخش</persName>
                  <gap/></mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div> 
         <div corresp="#orig_div3"  xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><gap/> <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">Ibrahim</persName> true servant of Sultan <persName ref="#muradBakhsh">Murad Bakhsh</persName></mentioned></stamp>
            </p></div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1654_dai_lns235ms_j_v.jpg"/> 
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>   
               بتاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus"><num>۴</num>
                  شهر صفر سنه
                  <num>۲۸</num>
               </date>
               <gap/>
               نقل بدفتر  
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div4"  xml:id="trans_div4"> 
            <p>On the <date calendar="#julus">4th of the month of Safar in the year 28</date>, a copy [reached] the office.</p>
         </div>
         
